import React from "react";
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Switch,
  Route,
  Link
} from "react-router-dom"

import TemplateDefault from './templates/Default'
import Home from "./pages/Home"
import Customers from "./pages/Customers"
const App = () => {
  return (
  <TemplateDefault>
    <Router>
        <Switch>
          <Route path='/customers'>
            <Customers />
          </Route>
          <Route path='/'>
            <Home />
          </Route>
        </Switch>
    </Router>
  </TemplateDefault>
  )
}

export default App;
